{"tid":1868622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「三」唔係一個醫護，但處理過其他國家既罷工","createTime":"2020-02-07T16:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T07:29:44.000Z","uid":81236,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"dea6eed2ff1db1f78f00baec72c06b4d4b20489a","tid":1868622,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票宣布擱置罷工，其實有咩問題？大家有咩好嘈？<br />\n<br />\n1）繼唔繼續罷工係由投票決定，絕對係民主體現。<br />\n<br />\n2）呢個係醫護既罷工，唔係全港既大三罷，你又唔係有權罷工與否既一員，又有咩資格話人點解唔繼續罷工？<br />\n<br />\n3）唔好將你自己既意願同共同責任強加落願意挺身而出既人身上。<br />\n<br />\n4）罷工就救港，復工就救人。不論係罷工定復工，都會係對香港百利而無一害。<br />\n<br />\n5）今次醫護罷工係香港咁耐以來最成功同團結既一次，為日後組織罷工帶黎指標。 （你唔係諗住一次杖就成功掛？）<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n以下會講點解今次醫護罷工其實唔係輸哂<br />\n<br />\n一. 就組織而言，醫護罷工為大家做左次好好既示範。籌備時間雖短，但絕對唔馬虎。簽到等等為罷工既人注下強心針，唔再係網上鳩叫人「罷工、大三罷」<br />\n相信日後各工會會好好借鑑。<br />\n<br />\n二. 就「罷工」而言，唔再係濕鳩打工仔請病假留係屋企就當罷工，而係向公司表明係參與罷工，係一場真「罷工」。<br />\n<br />\n三. 雖然政府無全部妥協，但無醫護咁齊心罷工，加上手足送大禮比關口，絕對係唔係迫到政府一步一步讓步。<br />\n希望大家了解呢個係談判既藝術。<br />\n<br />\n四. 今日係醫護工會既投票決定是否繼續罷工，並非妥協或經談判下既交換條件。保留日後主導權。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n經過今次醫護罷工，希望對大家有啟示：<br />\n<br />\n甲. 大家應對緊既係一個暴政，唔單單係一間公司，你唔好諗住一時三刻佢就會跪低，即使醫護二萬個會員都罷工，政府都唔會第一時間回應你。<br />\n呢一場係耐力既對待。<br />\n<br />\n乙. 對抗是一定有代價，但妥協或不反抗既代價一定係更高。政府一定係連講句支援都唔會。<br />\n<br />\n丙. 「罷工」一定唔會係單一力量迫使政權妥協，即使「大三罷」都係。<br />\n<br />\n丁. 經過肺炎生死搏鬥，市民應該好明白呢個唔係政權死，就係市民亡既遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n感覺香港最終會經歷一場真革命，不論最終是否成功，絕大部份香港人只有係革命勝利中先可以存活落去。"},{"pid":"22ce7ef59dcb14e7c6eedbdfdbf53d40862514c0","tid":1868622,"uid":81236,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"醫護係以行業既名義罷工，但爭取全港人既福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n承受住大部分既壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befc9a7eed3a2ac98f7e603102f341de568227e7","tid":1868622,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:31:50.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffe994c3f077ab235dffe18ce5478f5ed01f103","tid":1868622,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f557c4edbdf428aba821234be5784ffd96f8ba66","tid":1868622,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345bdb2a96d47c7ed3e6e0d2d25c1bbdecc0a227","tid":1868622,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af0abececee5e88dedbe0963e8858646f1da33e9","tid":1868622,"uid":36122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e2660af6467dda38961046